    <div class=wrapper>
        <div class="container">
            <img src="https://app.consultingcockpit.com/assets/Consulting_cockpit_logo_peach-BMG-cAIO.webp" alt="Consulting Cockpit Logo" class="logo" />

            <h1>IT’S COMING...</h1>
            <h2>THE EARLY ACCESS TO THE NEWEST AGENCY OS</h2>

            <p class="intro">And you can be part of it.</p>

            <p>
            We are inviting <strong>100 bold entrepreneurs</strong> to get exclusive early access to the<br/> Consulting Cockpit. <br />
            </p>
    <p>
    If you are:
    <ul>
    <li>running a software agency</li>
    <li>hiring a team up to 20 employees or contractors</li>
    <li>ready to explore the unknown and build the future</li>
    </ul>

    </p>

            <p>
            Apply for an interview to join our Early Access program – and gain entry to the exclusive private Discord community of pioneering entrepreneurs like yourself.
            </p>

            <form class="signup-form">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Your first name e.g. John" required />
            <input type="email" placeholder="Your E-Mail address e.g. jd@mydomain.com" required />

            <div class="checkbox">
                <input type="checkbox" id="terms" required />
                <label for="terms">I accept Consulting Cockpit’s terms and conditions (<a href="/datenschutz">found here</a>).</label>
            </div>

            <button type="submit">Apply for Early Access</button>

            </form>
        </div>

        <Footer/>
    </div>
